## Default Stack Decisions (Opinionated)

### 1. Distribution

* Distribution before paid acquisition
* Partnerships before advertising
* Community before incentives
* Retention before expansion

### 2. Community

* Telegram for broad accessibility
* Discord for power users
* Ambassadors for early evangelism
* Contributors before moderators

### 3. Content

* X/Twitter as primary distribution channel
* Educational content over hype content
* Founder-led storytelling
* Consistent publishing cadence

### 4. Launches

* Waitlist before token incentives
* Product validation before scaling
* Community activation before TGE
* Retention before expansion

### 5. Metrics

* Retention over vanity metrics
* Active users over impressions
* Revenue over engagement
* Sustainable growth over short-term spikes

