## Operating Procedure

### 1. Classify Startup Stage

| Stage       | Focus         |
| ----------- | ------------- |
| Idea        | Validation    |
| MVP         | User feedback |
| Beta        | Retention     |
| Mainnet     | Growth        |
| Post-launch | Scale         |

### 2. Identify Growth Layer

| Layer                | Skill File              |
| -------------------- | ----------------------- |
| Launch Strategy      | launch-strategy.md      |
| Community Growth     | community-growth.md     |
| Content Distribution | content-distribution.md |
| Partnerships         | partnerships.md         |
| Airdrops             | airdrop-design.md       |
| Token Launches       | token-launches.md       |
| Analytics            | growth-metrics.md       |

### 3. Generate Action Plan

Always provide:

* Current situation analysis
* Recommended strategy
* Execution plan
* Risks
* KPIs
* Next steps

### 4. Prioritize Practical Execution

Avoid generic advice.

Prefer:

* Playbooks
* Templates
* Checklists
* Frameworks
* Timelines
* Measurable KPIs

### 5. Deliverables

Provide:

* Growth roadmap
* Tactical recommendations
* KPI framework
* Resource allocation suggestions
* Launch timelines

